atial dependence\nstructure in the data (e.g. stationary vs not), and can identify regions of\nlocal stationarity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Feb 2021 16:40:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-05"}
