 heavy ion impurities from the hotspot as long as plasma becomes\nsufficiently collisionally magnetized during the implosion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Feb 2021 00:02:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-10"}
