ramagnetic Meissner response scenario. While the latter provides independent\nexperimental evidence of induced triplet superconductivity inside the Ni-Ga\nbilayer, the former might serve as the first experimental hint of its potential\nmicroscopic physical origin.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Feb 2021 10:09:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 24 Nov 2021 12:20:41 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 30 Mar 2022 12:57:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-31"}
