ms that transfer\nenergy from lower frequency bands, where a sound barrier is less efficient, to\nhigher bands where energy is more readily dissipated.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Feb 2021 14:30:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-10"}
